┌ Help ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  nav  next/prev                                                      │
│  i / o               cycle unit finer / coarser (section ↔ paragraph │
│↔ line ↔ sentence ↔ word)                                             │
│  Space / Backspace   synonyms for i / o                              │
│  j / k               next / prev anchor in active unit               │
│  ↓ / ↑ / → / ←       synonyms for j / k                              │
│  ]/[                 next/prev annotation                            │
│                                                                      │
│  I  AST view        O  links                                         │
│  /  search          n/N  next/prev match                             │
│  c  change (literal)                                                 │
│  f  feedback (intent)                                                │
│  b  a  insert before · after                                         │
│  e  edit existing change/feedback                                    │
│  x  clear annotation, or strike (sentence mode only)                 │
│  r  copy result to clipboard                                         │
│  q  Q          quit (confirm y/n) · silent quit                      │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
